    <artifactId>truevfs-kernel-spec</artifactId>

    <name>TrueVFS Kernel Specification</name>
    <description>
        Specifies the API for accessing the federated virtual file system space.
        Most noteably, the specification contains a service provider API for a
        singleton file system manager, an I/O buffer pool and a file system
        driver map.
    </description>

